Hadith.1698 - Imam (as) said, regarding the words of Allah (swt), the Exalted:
"There is no good in most of their secret talks except one who enjoins charity or kindness or reconciliation between people" (Surah An-Nisa 4:114);
"Kindness (ma'ruf) refers to lending."

